snippet.title: Octopus City Blues Trailer 3
snippet.description:
Add Octopus City Blues to your Steam wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1192230/

A big thank you to @bitmapkid for editing this trailer. Make sure to subscribe and check out their videos!

This trailer was first shown during the @SixOneIndie September 2024 showcase. You can watch the full thing here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P38Qv3Ee5Ek
